"url_meta":{"origin":43601,"position":0},"title":"Anas on Dua: Praying for family after finishing the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 1, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Thabit reported: Anas ibn Malik, may Allah be pleased with him, when he completed reading the entire Quran, he would gather his children and his household and supplicate to Allah for them. Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 3517 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064e\u062b\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u062a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37601,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/23\/zayd-recitation\/","url_meta":{"origin":43601,"position":1},"title":"Zayd on Quran: Recitation for contemplation better than for completion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 23, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Yahya ibn Sa\u2019id reported: A man came to Zayd ibn Thabit, may Allah be pleased with him, and he said, \u201cHow do you view reciting the entire Quran in seven days?\u201d Zayd said, \u201cThat is good, but to recite it in half a month or ten days is more beloved\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33438,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/12\/umar-convinces-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":43601,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Mushaf: Umar convinces Abu Bakr to collect the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Thabit reported: Abu Bak sent for me after the people of Al-Yamamah were killed and Umar ibn al-Khattab was with him. Abu Bakr, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cUmar came to me and said that many reciters of the Quran were killed in the fighting at\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27536,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/11\/prophet-revises-quran-itikaf\/","url_meta":{"origin":43601,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: The Prophet reviews the Quran in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would review the Quran once every year in Ramadan, and he reviewed it twice in the year he passed away. The Prophet would retreat in the mosque for ten days every year, and he secluded himself for twenty days\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25799,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/22\/ayat-rajm-not-written-kitab\/","url_meta":{"origin":43601,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Rajm: Verse of stoning not meant to be in Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Kathir ibn al-Salt reported: Amr ibn al-\u2018As and Zayd ibn Thabit would write down the Quran. They passed over this verse, and Zayd said, \u201cI heard the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, say: The married old man and old woman, if they commit adultery, then stone\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32703,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/07\/ali-three-baqarah-before-bed\/","url_meta":{"origin":43601,"position":5},"title":"Ali on Quran: Recite last three verses of al-Baqarah before bed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ishaq reported: Ali, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cI have not seen anyone of intelligence go to sleep until he had recited these three verses at the end of Surat al-Baqarah.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 3289 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Nawawi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0625\u0650\u0633\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0642 \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0644\u064a\u0651\u064d \u0631\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/43601","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/po